These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, family, satire, western, zombie
There are 5 different favourite colors: chestnut, amber, azure, blue, blood-red
The people use 5 different means of transport: tram, bus, car, quad-bike, helicopter
 1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person driving the tram is the person watching crime movies##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person driving the car##1
11. the person drinking tea is between the person who likes amber and the person watching zombie movies##2
12. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
13. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up        | almond-milk | tea     | coffee   | lemonade |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | family      | western | zombie   | crime    |
| Color   | blue  | amber     | chestnut | azure | blood-red  |
| Transport           | bus | car      | helicopter     | quad-bike   | tram     |

