.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: gardening, hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
There 5 different types of food: radish, cucumber, pear, carrot, peas
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, indian, polish, spanish
There are 5 different favourite colors: lilac, emerald, grey, purple, mauve
 1. the person who likes mauve is in the middle##1
 2. the person eating peas is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person who likes emerald is between the chinese and the person eating peas##2
 6. the person who likes purple is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 7. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
 8. the indian is the person eating carrot##1
 9. the indian is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
10. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
11. the indian is the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | gardening | writing    | hiking  | reading    |
| Food   | peas    | cucumber       | pear      | radish | carrot        |
| Nationality   | spanish   | dutch     | chinese    | polish  | indian     |
| Color     | grey    | emerald | mauve | purple | lilac |

