.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
5 different games are played: whist, snooker, monopoly, poker, go
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, family, martial-arts, superhero
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, metal, pop, reggae
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, cola, soy-milk, sprite
 1. the person playing go is the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of pop is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person playing go is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person playing snooker is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 7. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking fanta is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
12. the person playing poker is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
13. the person drinking sprite is between the person watching superhero movies and the person playing monopoly##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Game         | whist | go     | monopoly   | snooker   | poker |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | documentary | adventure | martial-arts | family        |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | gospel      | pop       | reggae       | ambient       |
| Beverage         | lemonade | sprite  | soy-milk    | fanta    | cola        |

