.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, soy-milk, sprite, water
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, june, october, december, february
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: salsa, punk, techno, house, jazz
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, rowing, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the person drinking water is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the fan of jazz##1
 8. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the fan of techno##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
11. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's sport is baseball##2
12. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the fan of house##1
13. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | water      | sprite   | fanta   | soy-milk   |
| Birthday   | february    | december   | october   | june | january     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | techno     | house   | jazz | punk |
| Sport         | badminton | volleyball | baseball | rowing  | skiing     |

