The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, ship, skateboard, taxi
 1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 2. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the rat is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the owner of the horse is between the person traveling to paris and the person eating raspberry##2
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 6. the person traveling to london is in the middle##1
 7. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
 8. the person eating grapes is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the pony is the person eating onion##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
12. the owner of the dog is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
13. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
