 2. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the fan of country is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the fan of country##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the person playing go is on the far left##1
11. the fan of disco is between the person playing go and the person who's hobby is reading##2
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | juice       | mirinda    | soy-milk | iced-tea  | 7up        |
| Hobby       | video-games | card-games | reading  | traveling | drawing    |
| Game       | go        | poker   | chess  | mah-jongg   | whist |
| Music-Genre   | punk       | disco      | salsa      | blues | country  |

