.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, milk, sprite
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, rowing, golf, ice-hockey
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, old-henry, havana, bongani, siglo
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, hip-hop, house, trance
 1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
 2. the person who's sport is golf is between the havana-smoker and the person who's sport is rowing##2
 3. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is golf##1
 4. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the fan of house##1
 5. the game-smoker is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the fan of blues##2
 7. the fan of house is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
11. the person who's sport is rowing is the old-henry-smoker##1
12. the bongani-smoker is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola         | milk      | iced-tea | sprite     |
| Sport           | cycling | rowing | golf | ice-hockey    | biathlon  |
| Cigar   | bongani  | old-henry    | game | havana    | siglo |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | blues        | ambient   | house    | trance     |

