.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, musical, zombie, drama
City: boston, venice, london, rome, marseilles
5 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, helicopter, jet-ski, ship
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 3. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person traveling to boston and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
 7. the person watching musical movies is between the person driving the airplane and the person watching drama movies##2
 8. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching adventure movies##2
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Movie-Genre         | drama  | musical | zombie   | animation      | adventure |
| City   | boston   | rome    | venice | marseilles | london      |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | goldfish    | cat       | lizard     | mouse      |
| Transport     | helicopter | ship        | airplane  | car        | jet-ski    |

