.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  project-manager, designer, paramedic, photographer, teacher
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy, martial-arts, musical, thriller
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, electronic, reggae, rock
There 5 different types of food: pineapple, kiwi, strawberry, lettuce, peach
 1. the project-manager is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is between the person eating lettuce and the fan of rock##2
 3. the fan of rock is on the right of the teacher##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is the fan of ambient##1
 5. the fan of ambient is between the person eating peach and the fan of electronic##2
 6. the person eating peach is on the right of the teacher##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the fan of reggae##1
 8. the photographer is the fan of blues##1
 9. the person eating pineapple is the fan of blues##1
10. the photographer is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the designer##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Job         | paramedic    | teacher  | designer  | project-manager      | photographer |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | thriller   | musical | martial-arts | documentary   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | ambient    | rock    | reggae       | blues         |
| Food   | lettuce  | kiwi | peach    | strawberry     | pineapple      |

 